{"tid":2035556,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭定康倡國安法納G7議程","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:11:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e66d35da7b2f749d76413f1e558af5b60fdad24a","tid":2035556,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/TH575QOGF2TLB5OWII6KTOU4SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FTH575QOGF2TLB5OWII6KTOU4SU%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5qf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=cd53775d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FTH575QOGF2TLB5OWII6KTOU4SU%2F&h=9e6059ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/TH575QOGF2TLB5OWII6KTOU4SU/</a><br />\n<br />\n彭定康倡國安法納G7議程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n末代港督彭定康前日在英國《金融時報》撰文，表示英國應確保中國強推「港版國安法」列入今年七大工業國集團（G7）峯會討論議程。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康在文章中指，英國及其G7盟友應堅決反對中國國家主席習近平的政權，並稱之為「開放社會的敵人」。彭定康寫道，「當世界其他國家專注對抗武漢肺炎疫情之際，他（習近平）卻在撕毀《中英聯合聲明》─一份在聯合國秘書處登記、保證香港資本主義制度和生活方式50年不變的條約」。此外，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200526/large/1590424650_d669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590424650_d669.jpg&h=dd1f40e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭定康指，英國及其G7盟友應堅決反對習近平的政權。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德議員：一國兩制形同虛設<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳景生轟等同改《基本法》<br />\n<br />\n德國執政黨基民盟的國會外交委員會主席勒特根稱，。。。。。。。。。香港局勢將進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》評論認為，。。。。。。。。。。唯一答案是全球結盟支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》/《泰晤士報》/美國《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"327e8cb9813a2c7f8e4af7768135e8662d8b5334","tid":2035556,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25714cd4d24b1888a37cdd7ef307429cc8c4cbd0","tid":2035556,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65383fdc31217ca280d85df9556efc70e1d5119e","tid":2035556,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"成日話英美煽動,洗腦後生仔,事實上彭定康比所有中國人,4成香港人,一眾狗官,共匪更愛香港"}]}